        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Padua Score &ge;4 points - Pharmacologic prophylaxis is indicated. If high risk of bleeding, use mechanical prophylaxis.</li>\n<li>Padua Score &lt;4 points - Pharmacologic prophylaxis is <b>not</b> indicated, consider using mechanical prophylaxis.</li>\n</ul>",
